    {
      "id": "1b34750c-f3ba-8017-979f-d6bc9cfa64cc",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Author investigates how to build trust in these recommenders: i) user perception, ii) designing interventions to build trust, iii) multidimension approach to building trust. ",
